    <title>About this Manual</title>
    <conbody>
        <section>
            <p>This manual describes how system operators can install, operate, maintain, and monitor FUJITSU ServerView <ph
            conref="../../shared/product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Name"/>.
               <!-- - hereafter referred to as <ph
                    conref="../../shared/product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Name"/> (<ph
                    conref="../../shared/product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"/>). --></p>
            <p>The manual is structured as follows: </p>
            <p>
                <table
